Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首曲子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蒙？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫左慈的男人… 為什麼會唐突地做出那種事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非他認識我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和左慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那傢伙並不是左慈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的真名是王允子師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王允子師？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去 你的存在對那傢伙而言就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用勉強告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我並不覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我看得出你有些難受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五話 非危不戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大·海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是來這裏做什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您忘記了嗎 伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 大海在召喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒召喚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你們好好幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃雪糕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我二支
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這兼職？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BOY 接下來有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵一碗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得提不起勁來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼懲罰遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤得呱呱叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得來到海邊 怎麼能和玉米一起被烤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞成這樣 你要怎麼賠償？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這位是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽怯吧 這位可是罩著這片海濱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生 摸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…PP
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太丟人了 我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是摸摸而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是所謂的『SKINSHIP』嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}『SKINSHIP』：日式英語 大致是通過肌膚的觸碰來增進感情\N和肌膚之親有區別，大多是母親撫摸孩子以增進母子情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是十足的性騷擾吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好委屈 伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們2個可不像是姐妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這玩意還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹惹得禍 姐姐就得好好承擔起責任才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白摸我重要的妹妹的PP 得好好給我負起責任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1…2…3…4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2…2…3…4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們2個在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易可以開懷暢遊的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的地方都搞沒了 這都是拜誰所賜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 伯符還真是個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…公瑾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個最合適了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 如果我要做好便當帶過來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會遇到這種事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是仲謀的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是份提供伙食的兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就只帶了回程的車費
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了日光浴女王大賽結果的發表時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的日光浴女王是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九號參賽者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關羽雲長小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我參賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是專門為關姐準備的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10萬日元我們就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我有事情想問老張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要穿校園泳衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為你說課外學習要延長嗎 你這個敗事有餘的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有一件泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不還是一樣的校園泳衣嗎 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸圍的大小不同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孔？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我穿這種大小的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在小看我嗎 笨蛋 絕不饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果獲勝的話 那筆獎金要買多少件泳衣都可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐上的話絕對是優勝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油 關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫策伯符…遇難了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫策小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 劉劉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}買泳衣的錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不怪仲謀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是和平時一樣 都怪伯符的傻瓜行為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你剛才說我是傻瓜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在這種時候是順風耳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前幾天的和解會上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於孫權小姐的便當款待 我們還沒有回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 你在看什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫策那傢伙又大肆胡鬧了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以被炒魷魚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過很符合她的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們是不是在什麼地方游泳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得過來 我們也去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不了多久就能見到孫策她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強迫似地邀請別人過來自己卻…那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐 感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像忘記了什麼似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位少女 是叫孫權嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常有規矩 根本無法想像她與孫策是姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 料理做得也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫策呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得她會做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好彈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盒子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非這是什麼的地圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是藏寶地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶藏就藏在前面的鐘乳洞裏面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可得去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶藏 寶藏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還留了個好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這位是誰嗎 膽怯吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們這樣的總是遇到強悍女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙和剛才的爆乳一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆乳？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個爆乳女現在去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才我看到 她前往鐘乳洞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何去那邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裏過去的話 划船比較快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意的話 我們的船可以借給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致子姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去尋寶 小孔就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這些全都是寶藏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:14:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是石灰石在發光而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又叫我笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好感動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？…都去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,財寶 財寶 你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 就好像是漲潮一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德 注意腳下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲謀…在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又走回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 劉備小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海水還真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲謀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 去哪裡了 那個敗事有餘的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劉備小姐不下來游嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？我不會游泳…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這個地方這麼漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼沒有人來這邊玩呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫權小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劉備小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫子有言…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趙雲 玄德她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 軍師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲謀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞錯路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無需這麼鄭重其事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們2個先上船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的『發勁』是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說她是呂布奉先？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說她為了置董卓仲穎於死地 自己舍棄了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這傢伙還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不巧 她喪失了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喪失記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她的身上完全感受不到那天的殺氣 就是這個原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那『發勁』的威力…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這傢伙就是呂布奉先的話 那就解釋得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得曾經和我交過手了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有沒有印象 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫子有言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『必以全爭於天下』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能接納過去的敵人 則終有一日將稱霸天下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日之敵即今日之友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且呂布小姐可是我的救命恩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣大家就都是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果這張地圖標注的是鯊魚的出沒地點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 老張
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去尋寶的經歷就是一段美好的回憶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶？我對這種連肚子都墊不了的東西沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的我一定也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:20:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 會讓你見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的君主 曹操孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道的話 就要幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏侯淵妙才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這條命是孟德的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時…我都與他…同生共死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說你肯幫了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫助我-王允子師与…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈元放
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是被姐姐搞壞的海濱店舖的請賠單
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我怎麼可能付得起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.55,0:23:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 讓關關用贏的那筆獎金先支援我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.20,0:23:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那筆獎金已經讓你全部吃光喝盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想把那筆錢用在我主玄德身上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？劉劉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用那錢給劉劉買什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣？內衣？還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 再問下去就有些不解風情了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六話 以上智為間者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}出自《孫子兵法》：故惟明君賢將，能以上智為間者，必成大功
